http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/mumbai/Chhota-Rajan-to-appear-before-MCOCA-court-via-video-conferencing/article13984779.ece

History sheeter Rajendra Nikalje alias Chhota Rajan, who is wanted in 71 cases in Maharashtra, will be produced in a special MCOCA court via video conferencing on Thursday.Police sources confirmed to The Hindu that a decision had been taken to produce him via video conferencing instead of bringing him to Mumbai in response to the production warrant against him.The J Dey murder case is scheduled for hearing on Thursday.